    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demo Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On his way back home, lost in the mountains, Barren encounters an adventurer near a mysterious temple. This is Kai, a young man who set out with his friends in search of an ancient treasure belonging to the Laman, a civilization that coexisted with the people of Kaodi for decades before being exiled long ago.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After an incident inside the temple, only Kai has managed to escape. Now, he asks Barren to rescue his companions…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/19fc9575a03a4eae7e3b6c8cac8d9221.avif?t=1740078746\" width=750 height=122 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/e1f381c2947fa05886c7430c97f795d9.poster.avif?t=1740078746\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/e1f381c2947fa05886c7430c97f795d9.webm?t=1740078746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/e1f381c2947fa05886c7430c97f795d9.mp4?t=1740078746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaodi is a short story about the scars that war leaves on the world and on hearts. After being instrumental in the victory against the Shan Republic, Barren must return home on a path filled with guilt, trauma, self-doubt, friendships and broken loyalties.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/21228959d9cc108f667c3ad9ee6bf4c6.poster.avif?t=1740078746\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/21228959d9cc108f667c3ad9ee6bf4c6.webm?t=1740078746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/21228959d9cc108f667c3ad9ee6bf4c6.mp4?t=1740078746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with a wide range of characters. Each will offer a new perspective on the devastation of war: stories of loss, dignity, forgiveness....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/7cf6663c733b26763e62059ff7ea06e0.poster.avif?t=1740078746\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/7cf6663c733b26763e62059ff7ea06e0.webm?t=1740078746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/7cf6663c733b26763e62059ff7ea06e0.mp4?t=1740078746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All seasoned with a beautiful low-spec artwork, a mix of traditional pixel-art with 3D modeling techniques and effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325580/extras/19fc9575a03a4eae7e3b6c8cac8d9221.avif?t=1740078746\" width=750 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
